{"title":"江城子 访延安","authors":["张志明"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":4,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"江城子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"访延安"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张志明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已巳三月，访圣地延安，登宝塔山远眺，心潮澎湃，抚今忆昔，夜不成寐，赋以志之。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长征万里史无前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤人间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跸延安。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千古难寻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窑小著雄篇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃马扬鞭战鼓响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千军动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定江山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为教日月换新天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任在肩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路艰难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毋忘英烈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碧血染黄泉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜看延河东流去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"润神州，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"色斑斓！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}